channel.title: Does anyone know how to do a cold water extraction?
channel.description: Does anyone on here have any experience in CWE's with Hydrocodone? I looked it up and I think I can proceed into doing it but I just want to know if anyone has any tips or something over it. I also have no clue what the hydrocodone/water ratio is, and I would like to know it.

item.title: Does anyone know how to do a cold water extraction?
item.dc:creator: @ziplock ziplock
item.description:
@ziplock wrote:

[quote=“The Reaper X, post:4, topic:350066”][quote author=ziplock link=topic=446434.msg3277750#msg3277750 date=1279664986]

[quote author=The Reaper X link=topic=446434.msg3277667#msg3277667 date=1279659169]

Does anyone on here have any experience in CWE’s with Hydrocodone? I looked it up and I think I can proceed into doing it but I just want to know if anyone has any tips or something over it. I also have no clue what the hydrocodone/water ratio is, and I would like to know it.
[/quote]What are you doing? I thought hydrocodone was a pain medication?..

Yes but my life sucks and I’m stressed out and it gives an amazing high when you use over recommended dosage.
[/quote]What the fuck? Then just take it? You don’t have to do an experiment… What mg are they?[/quote]

That mush APAP so often will cause me to go deaf. It’s a method of filtering out the APAP. I already did it and it worked so you can lock this if you want.
